This is the source list for the shooting game created in Chapter 2.
The parts that each file processes are as follows:

SHOOT.H                         Include files
ATARI.C ATARI.H                 Hit detection
BGPUT.C BGSCR.C BG.H            BG related routines
ENEMOVE.C ENEMOVE.H ENEMY.C 
ENEMY.H ENEPATTERN.C            Enemy Routines
ETC.C ETC.H                     Processing routines for titles, game over, etc.
EVENT.C EVENT.H                 Event Routines
GRAPHIC.C GRAPHIC.H             Background Star Routine
MAIN.C                          Main Routine
MAKEFILE                        Makefile
SUB.C SUB.H                     Various small functions
SHIP.C SHIP.H                   Movement routine for the player's ship and bullets
SOUND.C SOUND.H ZLIB.S ZLIB.H   Sound-related routines
